    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是开始节点，然后进入这个判断菱形。如果正常就发布，不正常就修复？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A[Start]",
        "B{Is it working?}",
